    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在一个以日本为主题的三消游戏全新演绎中。在这里，你不只是简单地滑动方块来组合，而是扮演一位技艺高超的忍者，使用各种武器对敌人发动攻击，同时策略性地团结盟友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320760/extras/9a1150657c4a87397b1cd0d5b7a5af56.poster.avif?t=1744973708\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320760/extras/9a1150657c4a87397b1cd0d5b7a5af56.webm?t=1744973708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320760/extras/9a1150657c4a87397b1cd0d5b7a5af56.mp4?t=1744973708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种武器都有独特的攻击模式，为你提供多样的战略选择来解谜。这样，你可以从多个角度应对每一个挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你熟练掌握所有武器，难度将逐步升级。敌人会开始设置陷阱，增加额外的复杂性，迫使你提前几步思考，以成功解开谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320760/extras/2a951d7c0b9721cda45872cca648c081.poster.avif?t=1744973708\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320760/extras/2a951d7c0b9721cda45872cca648c081.webm?t=1744973708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320760/extras/2a951d7c0b9721cda45872cca648c081.mp4?t=1744973708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有创意的三消玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20个任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个任务6个关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共计120个关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6种不同武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5种陷阱类型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日本主题游戏</p></li></ul>",
